{"tid":1831003,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［轉寄］唔好唔記得聽日係咩日子","createTime":"2020-01-20T05:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T05:31:08.000Z","uid":41366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe1c666b861d75597bd52aa6dee7f19d2680404","tid":1831003,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfX6GTi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkfX6GTi.jpg&h=5e991f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n121元朗黑夜半週年<br />\n日期 : 1月21日 (二)<br />\n時間 : 20:00<br />\n地點 : 元朗黨鐵站 / Yoho Mall<br />\n*網民自發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qm2ix0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqm2ix0p.jpg&h=df75c8c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>以我所知其他地區都有意搞係自己區黨鐵搞靜坐/其他活動<br />\n請注意各大公海</strong><br />\n<br />\n各位手足，雖然我地睇到琴日有隻便衣狗俾人打晒缸，好撚興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我哋唔好唔記得聽日呀<br />\n對家叫我地忘記721，我地就個個月都Mark實佢<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人</span>絕不善忘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，決一不可<br />\n黑警死全家，死晒男家死女家<br />\n死晒全家笑哈哈"},{"pid":"a59dba99a6629748c419838583afc734370272bd","tid":1831003,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"121，元朗見"},{"pid":"6222d7c907dce5a8459348f7192189a1dc845a7b","tid":1831003,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:31:08.000Z","msg":"121，元朗見"}]}